        "content": "<p>cfallin <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/5645#issuecomment-1406997500\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/5645\">issue #5645</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ah, that is indeed a bug if <code>uext</code> doesn't actually work! We'll look into this.</p>\n</blockquote>",
